msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Nintendo - SNES / SFC (bsnes 2014 Performance)"
msgstr "Nintendo - SNES / SFC (bsnes 2014 Performance)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "A libretro fork of bSNES. As close to upstream as possible.[CR][CR]The [I]Performance[/I] profile focuses more on execution speed than on accuracy."
msgstr "Verze odvozená od bSNES pro libretro. Snaží se zůstat co nejblíže upstreamu.[CR][CR]Profil [I]Performance[/I] se zaměřuje více na rychlost běhu než na přesnost."

msgctxt "Addon Disclaimer"
msgid "In loving memory of Near / Byuu"
msgstr "S láskou na památku Near / Byuu"
